Package: ai-system-assistant
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-pip, python3-pydantic
Recommends: ollama
Maintainer: AI System Assistant Team <contact@example.com>
Description: Local AI assistant for Ubuntu system management
 AI System Assistant is a local AI-powered tool for managing
 Ubuntu system tasks through natural language commands.
 .
 Features:
  - Start applications
  - Kill processes
  - List running processes
  - Restart systemd services
  - Execute safe shell queries
 .
 Uses Ollama with llama3 model for local AI processing.
 No cloud APIs or internet connectivity required at runtime.
